   "source": [
    "# VNA 控制"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**scikit-rf** 包含几个虚拟仪器类，这些类位于 `skrf.vi` 模块中。本页演示了对 VNA 的基本控制。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 连接并查询仪器 ID"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "```chinese",
    "from skrf.vi.vna import keysight",
    "",
    "instr = keysight.PNA(\"TCPIP0::192.168.0.2::INSTR\")",
    "instr.id",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 从 scikit-rf 网络对象中获取散射参数"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "```chinese",
    "ntwk = instr.get_snp_network()",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
